<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/20523390">怎样做能让一个不乐观的人变得乐观？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="389873" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content"></div>


</div>
